How to Install New Game+

This is our community's own desktop app — a custom client for our self-hosted Fluxer server. Follow these steps to get set up.

Step 1: Download

Download the app here: New Game+ Setup 1.0.0.exe

https://github.com/ExoticSquids/Fluxer-NG-Client/releases/tag/v1.0.0

Step 2: Run the installer

Double-click New Game+ Setup 1.0.0.exe to start the install.

Click More info (small grey text)
Click Run anyway


The installer will then open normally.

Step 3: Install


Choose where you want it installed (or just leave the default)
Click through the installer
A shortcut will automatically be added to your Desktop


Step 4: Open the app

Double-click the New Game+ icon on your Desktop (or find it in your Start menu).

It'll open straight into our server — log in or create an account, and you're in.

Step 5: Test your mic,  camera, streaming all of it. Its basically discord but you get all the premium stuff for free. 
